    "4007613": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We're back here again. So... Are we completely out of the mirage?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "How strange..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "My mirage didn't contain any hints on the Fatui or the machine... Does that mean they had nothing to do with these mirages after all?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Or perhaps these mirages are a mere consequence, and not part of a process at all?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Umm, Paimon's lost..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "I mean, these mirages were not steps towards solving the mystery, but rather a direct effect of whatever is going on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Someone did something to bring the mirages into being. As they were just passive side products, it was natural that they couldn't provide us with any useful information."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "In other words, those mirages were only about ourselves."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Hmm, pure materializations of ourselves... Interesting."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Everyone, maybe we should go back to where this whole thing began."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "#During our first day on the island, {NICKNAME} and I checked out the Fatui camp together. We found a strange machine there, as well as some disoriented Fatui."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is correct."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "The researcher who spoke to us claimed that the machine was just a Fatui industrial invention. He even promised to not disturb us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Right right, and the cappy-cap guy looked half asleep the entire time. He kept talking nonsense!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I wonder, is it possible that \"madness\" and \"mirages\" are two different outcomes of the machine's influence?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "If so, everything can be traced back to that damaged machine — except for the difference in how it affects people. This, I believe, is caused by differences between the affected people themselves."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "When you put it that way... it is indeed difficult to distinguish dreams and hallucinations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "So what you're saying is, the device affected us differently because we are different from the Fatui?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Yes, and according to our observations over these past few days, I think... the difference is that we all have stronger willpower."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "...Yeah, I can get behind that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xinyan",
                    "T": "People with strong willpower will hallucinate instead of falling into madness, but those who break too easily can't maintain a stable mirage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "In other words, we should go back to the Fatui camp and destroy that machine right away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "No, it should be repaired, rather than destroyed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "What mein Fräulein means is that rashly destroying a machine we do not understand may lead to more serious consequences. It would be better to find a way to repair it first."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Right, it pays to be cautious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "If my guess is correct, that machine is capable of influencing the human brain. So we'd better tread carefully."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So let's go now! There's no time to waste!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
